    <h3>District Information</h3>
    <p>With students as the number one priority, Alameda Unified School District believes in
excellence and equity for all. Their mission is to create an environment where students can
learn to think critically and acquire positive work habits, along with securing the attitude
and skills that are crucial to in becoming an effective and respectful citizen. An abundance
of diverse courses, clubs and athletic programs to join help solidify a feeling of belonging
and pride, which goes a long way in the future. With a highly dedicated staff working to
constantly improve the curriculum, Alameda Unified School District has proven to be a
success!</p>
   
